_sText:
trikz_khaos

A trikz t9 map

Gomes, who started this project a few months ago, dropped the idea and sent the files to me.

It was very hard for me to get the right distances and to think about the stages. I got some inspiration from other t8/9 trikz maps. It took me a few months to get the final version. I lost motivation many times during this hammer battle. I hope you guys have fun with this map!

Thanks a lot to everyone who helped testing and finding bugs (If I missed someone, please tell me). And if you find any bugs, please let me know too!
